subject: Tennis
Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Andy Murray’s 4-6, 7-6 (2), 6-1, 7-6 (2) victory was filled with extended rallies and memorable defense, but the differences in the end were Murray’s bigger serve and bolder tactics
